^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, let us review a couple of things we learned here. First, if you have a 2N rebid, make it, regardless of your major suit holdings. Of course, had I bid 1S, then Kerrie should bid 4S, not 2N. On the other hand, if you cannot raise partner's major, then bid 2N if you have 18-19 balanced, as it is very descriptive.|
