^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I mostly want to discuss the play, but will briefly discuss the bidding. Why did I not bid 2C since I have 4 hearts. With 4-3-3-3 distribution, often you make the same number of tricks in NT as in hearts or spades. And since 3N requires 9 tricks to 4H 10 tricks, I felt that 2N was warranted, particularly since I had such weak hearts.|
