NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now as to the play. There are several interesting and informative declarer technique issues here. First of all, at trick 1, Marge should play a low spade, not the 10. Why is that? Because suppose zewzew had a spade honor then if she got in and lead a spade through Marge, Marge might only get 1 spade tricks. But if Marge plays low, she is guaranteed 2 spade tricks. |
