^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, first let me discuss the auction. Should Anna bid 3H? It is not clear, but I think she should. By the law of total tricks they likely only have an 8 card fit. However, my competitive guidelines include the following If the opponents are at the 2-level with a known fit you should not be happy to let them play it there. So, even with an 8-card fit, you should push to the 3-level. |
